    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Micropsectra jokatertia Sasa et Ogata, 1999 and closely related species of the Micropsectra notescens species group; males, hypopygial diagnostic structures. A, E: M. junci (Meigen, 1818); B, F: M. rilensis Giłka, 2001; C, G: M. jokatertia; D, H: M. recurvata Goetghebuer, 1928. A–D: median and inferior volsellae, E–H: superior volsella and digitus." ;
